50|$|A Contact Approach is an {{approach}} available to aircraft operating on an <b>IFR</b> <b>flight</b> plan, where the pilot may deviate from the published {{instrument approach procedure}} (IAP) and proceed to the destination airport by visual reference to the surface.|$|R
